{"tid":793621,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"港姐老婆逆齡變索 50歲李克勤攰樣嚇親人","createTime":"2018-08-25T14:31:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T05:29:48.000Z","uid":29627,"like":333,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"71ad0ce135f833cce816ef80d27789f039c3585a","tid":793621,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:31:55.000Z","msg":"港姐老婆逆齡變索 50歲李克勤攰樣嚇親人 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180825/large/1535177546_0744.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180825%2Flarge%2F1535177546_0744.jpg&h=45a41716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陪住大家成長嘅藝人，好多，依家都，年過半百，或者近半百。女神方面有啱啱提到嘅47歲鍾麗緹，以及噚日53歲生日嘅羅霖；男方嘅代表，都有個半百李克勤。<br />\n<br />\n後來嗰陣嘅李克勤，係《淘氣雙子星》年代嗰個，一臉陽光唱《紅日》，或者用個前挺後趷唱「當年相戀意中人&hellip;」。有段時間佢留鬚扮滄桑，感覺似細路扮大人。<br />\n<br />\n依家李克勤真係踏入中年喇，曾經一段時間佢喺香港係空白咗，因為要北上。返嚟之後，好似又&hellip;&hellip;滄桑咗，眼袋嘅cup數越來越勁，臉上有敷mask都驅不散的倦意。 <br />\n<br />\n今日克勤太太盧淑儀又貼咗張一家人為盧爸爸慶祝生日嘅大合照，寫道：「今天是爸爸的70歲生日，爸爸生日快樂身體健康，長命百歲。還記得小時候你會跟我玩英文串字遊戲，帶我去大球場看足球，到郊野公園燒烤，去海灘游泳，打羽毛球，遊車河&hellip;&hellip;但你管教很嚴，小時候我很頑皮，喜歡講大話，但一給你發現就大懲罰⋯⋯藤條炆豬肉，跪地主，困我在洗手間裏。因為在你眼中道德，孝順父母，尊師重道，準時，誠實等⋯這種種都是做一個好人最基本的。」<br />\n<br />\n「到我現在已為人媽媽，我衷心感激你和媽媽對我們的教導，讓我們可以在開心和有家教的環境下成長。希望你也驕傲有我和弟弟妹妹在你生命裡。我愛你。」字裡行間充滿暖暖的愛意&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n克勤都有出席，囝囝個樣就遮住咗&mdash;&mdash;但大家焦點都離不開戴上Cap帽嘅克勤&mdash;&mdash;搞乜嘢啊？應該燈光問題啦，克勤仲要戴帽，陰影之下令佢好似俾歲月摧殘咗&hellip; <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180825/58606300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180825%2F58606300&d=DdDrCGpX2awB3FpcnDWBnsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=0ba5eaac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180825%2F58606300&h=a18ac942\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180825/58606300</a><br />\n<br />\n比老婆吸乾左採陽補陰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3019bfca0a5b413b7107170e6d513631a986c8ff","tid":793621,"uid":194177,"like":225,"dislike":4,"score":221,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:33:23.000Z","msg":"似有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90a6e31925db4e8bc394e21611919ad2be4f1d8","tid":793621,"uid":37524,"like":163,"dislike":5,"score":158,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"勤伯"},{"pid":"97ba77d0f05ad7e810f7dcf94e78e67c049b8add","tid":793621,"uid":28433,"like":126,"dislike":5,"score":121,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"番得大陸多 合理"},{"pid":"97bcb567067cc3c05b91f7c51c5021c359eba5f5","tid":793621,"uid":132587,"like":383,"dislike":9,"score":374,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"佢連個樣都咁忠於曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e1c3b21c71825c73b89c412d7eae305b6f36b3","tid":793621,"uid":203589,"like":21,"dislike":5,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:44:44.000Z","msg":"嘩頂...<br />\n勤伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163797418defd5bc547e6a397305194aedf4f3c7","tid":793621,"uid":25560,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:52:07.000Z","msg":"近得譚伯多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d90c0839cde8f4699ff43cb7a7b5ac4c8111319","tid":793621,"uid":61281,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:55:36.000Z","msg":"個外父成個李+x <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c189bc6170a0389fddb1145d2a4b80c7b7be22b9","tid":793621,"uid":76098,"like":44,"dislike":3,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:56:22.000Z","msg":"左上係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"